{"tid":1049301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：《流浪地球》撐唔起 周日旺角零票房 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-03-06T07:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T07:30:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d22b70fea6e7e839e0844faeea399ed37fe84653","tid":1049301,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190306/20626950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F20626950&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=274f7476\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F20626950&h=d92605ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190306/20626950</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：《流浪地球》撐唔起<br />\n周日旺角零票房 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190306/large/a1105a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190306%2Flarge%2Fa1105a.gif&h=2cfa7f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民瘋傳零票房截圖。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n中共出動到外交部發言人華春瑩「推薦」嘅國產科幻電影《流浪地球》，喺內地係威係勢大收近45億元人仔，不過香港票房就好唔掂，之前內地官媒《環球時報》報道，《流浪地球》開畫後，旺角百老匯影院試過賣得七張飛，搞到民建聯、工聯會等要撲出嚟加入拯救《流浪地球》行列，大搞廿蚊包場催谷票房，不過似乎冇乜作用，最近就有網民貼咗一張《流浪地球》3號星期日戲院網上售票貼圖，成場連一張飛都冇人買，可謂奇景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190306/large/a1105b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190306%2Flarge%2Fa1105b.gif&h=a27578e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1962年日本電影《妖星哥拉斯》。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被指抄襲1962年日片<br />\n<br />\n好多網民日前係網上貼出剛過去嘅星期日，旺角百老匯影院8點場《流浪地球》網上售票情況，張圖顯示全部座位一片綠，即係一張飛都買唔出，有網民揶揄零票房唔算奇，但一套內地收近45億元人仔、又吹噓到足以同荷李活科幻電影比拼嘅「大片」，竟然淪落到同爛片一樣命運，呢個先係奇景。<br />\n<br />\n之後陸續有網民貼出《流浪地球》喺不同戲院不同時段只賣出幾張飛嘅售票截圖，又有人貼《流浪地球》疑似抄1962年日本電影《妖星哥拉斯》嘅報道，揶揄一定係日本人坐時光機去抄襲中國電影，有網民直頭話《流浪地球》快趣落畫，否則Captain Marvel上畫後，可能每一場都係零票房喎。  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：錯字唔知掛起唔發覺 民建聯盲撐「開日大嶼」 (李八方)"},{"pid":"2ac893d93e9ffde748f5c662f4534c968973532a","tid":1049301,"uid":51127,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"好快會有愛國團體包場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba879ccd5d9b5ed7c7a3a5a23e8aa3ae918f1aa","tid":1049301,"uid":2267,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"以奶共嘅政府，我反而覺得喺落畫後啲戲院會公佈票房總收入有過千萬嘅成績。貼錢都要有呢堆數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351ba65ec91d72623a5d700067cf827ce362435a","tid":1049301,"uid":3457,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2ac893d93e9ffde748f5c662f4534c968973532a","tid":1049301,"uid":51127,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"好快會有愛國團體包場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:46:15.000Z","msg":"你要派飛先可能得小貓三四隻 <br />\n我派都唔會去 trailer太劣質 <br />\n睇都唔想睇 加下睇戲已經貴 <br />\n比幾百蚊 唔值得"},{"pid":"8722297a08ddec965ca644f3122e390d3fb86577","tid":1049301,"uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ac893d93e9ffde748f5c662f4534c968973532a","tid":1049301,"uid":51127,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"好快會有愛國團體包場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo